Triggers when the user right clicks an entity. \nThe target entity will be set as the interacted entity
Triggers when the user kills an entity. \nThe target entity will be set as the killed entity
Triggers when the user launched a projectile. \nThe target entity will be set as the launched projectile
Triggers when the user moves. \nThe location will be set as the location the user moves to

Triggers when the user jumps
Triggers when the user exits the server

Triggers when the user sneaks
Triggers when the user spawns
Triggers when the user starts or stops sprinting
Triggers when the user swaps hands

Triggers when the user targets an entity. \nThe target entity will be set as the target
